  "title": "Assistant Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<p>Create designs to entice consumers for the online retail market.</p><p><strong>Primary duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Design banners and online collaterals</li><li>Create outstanding visuals for daily write-up</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>West area</li><li>Proficient in computer skills, especially an in-depth knowledge of Adobe Photoshop or Illustrator</li><li>Excellent spoken & written communication skills in English and be able to bring forth his/her ideas succinctly.</li><li>Excellent interpersonal skills</li><li>Able to handle stress well and be comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Mature, confident, pro-active, organized and self-motivated</li><li>Excellent team player and ability to multi-task</li><li>Polytechnic diploma holders and candidates w/o experiences are welcomed to apply.</li></ul>",
